{"tid":741681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班警涉偷拍裙底 稱遭同袍插贓嫁禍","createTime":"2018-07-14T01:07:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-14T02:46:53.000Z","uid":35814,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e1afd7c8b910b9f13e1aedc309b88194f8218e1b","tid":741681,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T01:07:33.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】休班警去年涉在旺角港鐵站扶手電梯，涉嫌以重複將腳踏前的方法偷拍女子裙底影片，就「作出有違公德的行為」罪受審。他昨自辯時聲稱在其鞋上找到的攝錄機，乃由拘捕他的警員放上，「佢（警員）屈我嘅」。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n案件押後至8月17日裁決。原駐守水警西分區、現已被警隊停職的被告英裕泰（34歲）昨自辯稱，案發前兩天買了兩部攝錄機，以用作航拍或行車紀錄儀，惟懷疑攝錄機未能運作，遂打算拿回店舖更換。他稱去年1月21日下班後到旺角取波鞋，其後打算到深水埗買讀卡器及轉換器，以測試該兩部攝錄機，當時攝錄機放在其褲袋內。<br />\n<br />\n被問片段何來 稱買二手機<br />\n<br />\n被告續說，當到達旺角站時突記起要為5日後生日的兒子買蛋糕及禮物，遂乘電梯返回地面，惟其後遭警員從後拍膊頭及勒頸，他失平衡跌倒地上，再被拉至牆邊拘捕。被告稱當時因被拉跌後腦位置撞地，感到頭暈，被帶到旺角站警務室後，他被要求脫鞋，其後警署警長問有關片段是否他拍攝，被告當時只稱「我二手新買番嚟，我唔知你講咩」。<br />\n<br />\n稱脫鞋檢查 遭裝攝錄機<br />\n<br />\n被告又解釋，因想「睇下佢（警員）想點先」，故被搜出委任證前，也沒表明警察身分。被告認為拘捕他的警員因怕他投訴拘捕時濫用武力，才會「將我證供完美化」，強調脫鞋讓警方檢查時沒有攝錄機，而是警員稍後「放落去」。據了解，涉案攝錄機大小如紙包裝香口膠。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：WKCC203/18】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180714/s00002/1531506618622\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180714%2Fs00002%2F1531506618622&d=bJxTfcuo2CwFfVN18A5NBP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=b59c2784\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180714%2Fs00002%2F1531506618622&h=a078a37b\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180714/s00002/1531506618622</a>"},{"pid":"95c450ab4f3b961f1308715f982b0f9b15e03ec5","tid":741681,"uid":41524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T01:08:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e85260e634e1fc958611b6d777f01c076aa7d20","tid":741681,"uid":17622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T01:13:53.000Z","msg":"咁撚假都講得出，毅進仔冇得救"},{"pid":"ffd34f6c42015f65cede8e54d2092a48a4a24e7e","tid":741681,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T01:41:41.000Z","msg":"男人做得出唔怕認 做狗做到你咁無恥都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f396bd069ff45ce68292a160a75c51b59a8e98cd","tid":741681,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T01:43:24.000Z","msg":"阿sir嫁禍人唔駛你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d507f77a8c3f8fbfac90c389ca29cc44e64da24","tid":741681,"uid":59511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T01:47:44.000Z","msg":"打和啦，一齊坐就岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73bf52ff8df66bcab8763ece0863d2a7123f9b0f","tid":741681,"uid":953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T01:52:34.000Z","msg":"就算告邊一方都冇死， 連登仔又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f715f426d82719fc1957003eefde4a1cfd8f44c","tid":741681,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T01:53:13.000Z","msg":"是旦啦 你地冇做錯到"},{"pid":"2f4ef975269e2f488d59e85d3269cab9e9ad6bfb","tid":741681,"uid":22624,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T02:21:21.000Z","msg":"無論真定假，都一定有一個差佬犯法<br />\n<br />\n香港警賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4716094fcb11af13dc0b45e77d0fc6e46a1e33","tid":741681,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T02:42:59.000Z","msg":"阿sir狗咬狗唔洗你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff81afcc9201fd53803ea8d0fc7e33f012499ad0","tid":741681,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T02:46:53.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗骨既典範"}]}